snippet.title: TODAY'S SEARCH FOR SUMMER WELLS #SUMMERWELLS
snippet.description:
Cam, Alli and @Chasing talk about what is going on today in the Beech Creek community as search teams and law enforcement are combing the area looking for anything that might lead to finding Summer.
